                     <interp inst="t18510203-609-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 bottle, and 1 1/2 pint of cloves, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510203-name-799" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18510203-name-799" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18510203-name-799" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
