                        <interp inst="t18510203-name-802" type="surname" value="BARBER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18510203-name-802" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BARBER</persName>
                  </hi>. I was employed painting at the Druids' Arms, out<lb></lb>side the first-floor window, and saw the prisoner come out with a gilt show bottle under his coat—a female and a young man went in with him.</p>
